title: Orava is good, a song tells us. Is it?
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
The region is known for Orava Castle. But have you gone on a cruise in Námestovo or tasted some scrumptious ice cream in Dolný Kubín? 

Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec 
Guest: Vladimír Klocok, Tamari Mikatsadze, Tatia Basilaia, Jozef Ferenčík
